snippet.title: LCD DREAM ESCALATOR (Preview)
snippet.description:
LCD DREAM ESCALATOR is a walk-em-up mixtape with many rooms.

Play here: https://hydezeke.itch.io/lcd
Submission for Ludum Dare 49, theme: 'Unstable'

"What am I going to do with all this money??"
"Some rats appear to be bigger than others."
"I hear bubbling."
